Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.02,0:01:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在第二界層\N找到的真實之鏡是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的真實之鏡竟是個湖!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.95,0:01:45.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湖水復原了的湖面\N就像鏡一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.53,0:01:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我竟沒想過呢\N用骷髏魔神的死神也打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.41,0:01:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令第二界層恢復正常的我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.45,0:01:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於向第三界層出發了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.37,0:02:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也會是又有趣又有型呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.91,0:02:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十一話\N灼熱的一劍決勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.95,0:02:30.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏便是第三界層嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼也看不見呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.65,0:02:56.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.87,0:02:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被沙燒熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.42,0:03:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.64,0:03:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,你不熱嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.30,0:03:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.19,0:03:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心神合一的化便不覺得熱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.02,0:03:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱!  還是好熱!…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.35,0:03:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不陪你們了\N我才不想變燒鳥,再見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.04,0:03:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經這麼熱了,竟還點火把…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.04,0:03:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野牛武一郎流,火炎斬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.29,0:03:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,好厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.86,0:03:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害、厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.76,0:03:59.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好熱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真愚蠢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.05,0:04:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古路治湯母被消滅\N死神也被消滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只一會便來到第三界層了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.11,0:04:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所謂有第二次便有第三次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.67,0:04:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.46,0:04:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這位是第三界層的波士\N所也所也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.02,0:04:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然!第一界層和第二界層\N被攻破是第三次的失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.88,0:04:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個第三界層當渡的墓地\N才是最適合不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.29,0:04:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.90,0:04:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正如灼熱地獄這個名字一樣\N這裏會是他們的地獄呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多惡達大人的憤怒\N已到了爆炸之前了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.54,0:05:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定要收拾他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.99,0:05:10.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍作還未到嗎?劍作!\N喂!劍作在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.81,0:05:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直都在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.43,0:05:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡他們好像到了火熱村了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.18,0:05:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以離開一點嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.73,0:05:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪糕、冰棒、蘇打水…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.22,0:05:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說,只要想到便頭暈了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,便身忍法,火鍋鳥東
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咖喱飯、熱熱的小吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.46,0:05:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熱的時候吃熱的東西\N特別好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.56,0:05:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不要,頭暈更嚴重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.32,0:05:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊也是一樣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.35,0:06:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣也好,盡快找出\N令這第三界層復原的方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.25,0:06:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.63,0:06:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.36,0:06:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的魔兵,不能饒恕!\N去吧!奇怪珠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位沒事吧?有沒有受傷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.55,0:07:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖不知道你們是誰\N但很多謝你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.31,0:07:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是做\N我認為當然的事罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.58,0:07:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.82,0:07:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰說過可以停的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是多惡達的手下嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.63,0:07:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等,讓在下當你的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想看地獄嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.90,0:08:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來今天不分勝負呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但臉孔卻是我勝呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.27,0:08:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.97,0:08:54.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等,我叫你等等啊\N等…等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.40,0:09:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師…師傅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.59,0:09:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是觀音大使\N在下來到了極樂世界了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.62,0:09:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的我竟也可以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.10,0:09:17.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是溫柔,上到天國的感覺\N便是這意思嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.71,0:09:23.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅!師傅!師傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觀音大使,不要走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.40,0:09:35.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,振作點啊,師傅\N他是這條村的百合小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.59,0:09:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,百…百合小姐\N啊!等一等!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是失禮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.44,0:09:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,穿反了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.91,0:09:53.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,聽百合小姐說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.94,0:09:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個叫劍作的人\N令村民受了很多苦呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.06,0:10:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最嚴重的,除了這麼熱之外\N那些火把還不斷地增加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想它消掉的話\N便要勝過在下的劍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.31,0:10:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是普通人沒可能勝過他\N即使這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.60,0:10:21.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,村民裏也有\N渴望勝過他的人開始練劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果也是無法勝他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天也要被迫接受過分鍛煉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.22,0:10:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能饒恕\N竟令百合小姐受苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有封信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.48,0:10:55.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武一郎先生\N是劍作給你的挑戰書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.00,0:10:56.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.60,0:11:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我正求之不得\N這次我一定要收拾他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.46,0:11:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,你中暑了\N不要勉強啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.95,0:11:17.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…即使是這樣我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.30,0:11:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.12,0:11:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手,這是為了百合小姐…\N不,是為了正義啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.09,0:11:27.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師…師傅!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.69,0:11:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不去的話…不去的話不行的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好!由我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.09,0:11:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你剛才說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.08,0:11:40.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去和劍作決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.34,0:11:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.24,0:11:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.44,0:11:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不是你能打倒的對手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許是這樣\N但師傅你不是病倒了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.16,0:11:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.02,0:11:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那樣的話\N請你教我勝過劍作的方法吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.00,0:12:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍作他完全能夠看得見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.28,0:12:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是用劍的\N要戰勝他只有比他速度更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.13,0:12:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太慢了\N因為這樣流沙才會四散
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.33,0:12:35.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要比流沙的速度更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.41,0:12:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油,渡,是你的話\N一定可以做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.07,0:12:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?竟有此事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.79,0:12:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是沒用的\N不過所謂預防萬一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.74,0:12:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你去把那小鬼的劍處理掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.17,0:12:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說偷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.02,0:13:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍作那傢伙竟是這麼卑鄙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,怎樣可以取到手呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.56,0:13:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是單純的救世主呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.33,0:13:24.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鳥先生,你去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.56,0:13:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去了小便啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.12,0:13:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍不見了,師傅,起來啊\N勇者之劍不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.50,0:13:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你找清楚了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.15,0:13:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找清楚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.54,0:13:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他們搞的鬼嗎?\N為了什麼呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.25,0:13:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,怎辦好?\N叫不到龍神丸出來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藏在哪裏好呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.86,0:14:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算了,反正也不要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.72,0:14:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,決鬥是要分出生死的\N我不會留手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.08,0:14:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅的劍和我的劍\N感覺不同呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.52,0:14:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,儘管來吧,小鬼\N怎麼了?害怕了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.10,0:15:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忍法,尋找狗狗之術\N用這個來找渡的劍吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.87,0:15:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是磁石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.12,0:15:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用沙隱身嗎?\N可惡,去了哪裏呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.02,0:15:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了\N只要對著他的眼睛便行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.54,0:15:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,劍作!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.00,0:15:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裏嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.21,0:15:48.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊啊…這邊啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.20,0:15:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是時候了,劍作!這裏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.50,0:16:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.90,0:16:05.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了\N快令那些火台消掉,劍作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.14,0:16:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最討厭…便是輸了\N武道王者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是沙的巨浪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好,要叫戰神丸來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.20,0:16:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有空隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏沒有公共電話嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.20,0:17:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,你等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.08,0:17:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我忘了說,那邊是流沙沙漠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.00,0:17:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了!  進入火中的忍法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.73,0:17:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,忍法消防車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.67,0:17:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍…龍神丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勝利者只有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.90,0:18:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡!有了,接住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊!那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.52,0:18:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍神丸!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎樣?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.04,0:19:05.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快的動作呢\N好,再用一次剛才那招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.34,0:19:11.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你以為同樣的方法\N可以用兩次嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是那裏了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.00,0:19:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看不見他的動作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.01,0:19:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜點,渡\N你是為了什麼修煉到現在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了,要活用師傅教我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.85,0:19:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要用心眼去看\N要比流沙更快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你的話一定可以做得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.97,0:19:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?不攻過來的話\N便由我來攻了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.65,0:19:49.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會輸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.00,0:19:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.42,0:20:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.13,0:20:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,碰到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.64,0:20:05.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,渡,是剛才的時間性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.93,0:20:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混帳,今天我不會留手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.42,0:20:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,勾玉發光了\N又可以再用新招嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.21,0:20:22.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,名字是龍雷拳\N要用嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.54,0:20:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龍雷拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.17,0:20:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡,竟被這樣的東西\N破壞了感應器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的,動啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.50,0:20:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是機會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.20,0:21:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必殺!登龍劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.73,0:21:20.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最討厭便是輸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.30,0:21:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萬歲!勝了!萬歲!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.63,0:21:40.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有了火台\N令我們舒服了很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.09,0:21:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快我們會令這沙漠\N恢復一片翠綠的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.10,0:21:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在此之前要加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.41,0:21:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼再見了,師傅,走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.00,0:21:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我現在來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.50,0:21:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.15,0:22:08.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂!等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.04,0:22:10.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,師傅,快點吧!

